'''Jhank Shel''' was a [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] [[Kajidic/Legends|kajidic]]. The clan controlled the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lirra]] until the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], led by [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Heedra]], [[Subjugation of Lirra|drove them off]].

The Jhank Shel clan had originally taken control of Lirra in approximately [[100 BBY/Legends|100 BBY]] when the Hutts moved enough of their slaves to the planet to such a point that they outnumbered the original colonists.

